coding_ai_eval.question:
Given an integer n, for every positive integer i <= n, the task is to print,
"FizzBuzz" if i is divisible by 3 and 5, "Fizz" if i is divisible by 3, "Buzz" if i is divisible by 5 "i" as a string, if none of the conditions are true. Examples:
Input: n = 3 Output: ["1", "2", "Fizz"]
Input: n = 10 Output: ["1", "2", "Fizz", "4", "Buzz", "Fizz", "7", "8", "Fizz", "Buzz"]
Input: n = 20 Output: ["1", "2", "Fizz", "4", "Buzz", "Fizz", "7", "8", "Fizz", "Buzz", "11", "Fizz", "13", "14", "FizzBuzz", "16", "17", "Fizz", "19", "Buzz"]
